AREN'T REGULAR SYSTEM CRACKERS.
238
00:15:15,034 --> 00:15:18,304
HAY ALGO EXTRAÑO
ABOUT YOU, THAT'S FOR SURE.
239
00:15:18,304 --> 00:15:21,107
