AGAINST ALL ODDS
242
00:15:25,444 --> 00:15:28,047
TO MAKE THE ONLY TRUTH THERE IS
INTO A REALITY.
243
00:15:29,882 --> 00:15:31,884
- NO ENTIENDO.
244
00:15:31,884 --> 00:15:35,121
