WHEN YOU SAY "ONE TRUTH"?
245
00:15:35,121 --> 00:15:36,422
- WELL, IT'S LIKE
I SAID,
246
00:15:36,422 --> 00:15:38,424
REALMENTE NO SOY
A FORMAL KNIGHTS MEMBER.
247
00:15:38,424 --> 00:15:40,893
THEY NEVER REALLY
EXPLAINED IT TO ME.
248
00:15:40,893 --> 00:15:43,129
BUT THE ONE THING I DO KNOW
IS THAT IT'S TRUE.
249
00:15:43,129 --> 00:15:45,898
THE TRUTH HAS POWER FOR THE VERY
REASON THAT IT IS THE TRUTH.
250
00:15:45,898 --> 00:15:49,435
AND BECAUSE IT'S THE TRUTH, IT'S
CERTAIN THAT IT HAS TO BE JUST.
251
00:15:49,435 --> 00:15:51,437
IT'S PERSUASIVE,
ISN'T IT?
252
00:15:51,437 --> 00:15:53,940
NO PREFIERES TU VERDAD
LIKE THAT?
253
00:15:56,309 --> 00:15:59,212
I'M GOING.
SEE YA.
254
00:15:59,212 --> 00:16:02,315
CREO QUE MYU-MYU
IS REALLY JEALOUS OF YOU.
255
00:16:02,315 --> 00:16:03,850
DESPUES.
256
00:16:06,185 --> 00:16:08,454
- LOOK, TARO,
THANKS A LOT.
257
00:16:10,356 --> 00:16:12,058
- NO PROB.  LAIN.
258
00:16:12,058 --> 00:16:13,292
- EH?
259
00:16:24,337 --> 00:16:26,339
- HEY, IT'S A DATE.
AM I RIGHT?
260
00:16:26,339 --> 00:16:28,608
LIKE, I'M A GUY.
I JUST HAD TO DO THAT.
261
00:16:30,509 --> 00:16:33,346
